<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to SkillLink</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b7fff 0%, #1a5fd9 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #555555;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .features h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            padding-bottom: 18px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .feature-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b7fff 0%, #1a5fd9 100%);
            color: white;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .feature-text h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .feature-text p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b7fff 0%, #1a5fd9 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .cta-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .support-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .support-text a {
            color: #2b7fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888888;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2b7fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 8px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 6px;
            line-height: 36px;
            color: #555555;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to SkillLink <%= username %>! 🎉</h1>
            <p>Your gateway to talented student professionals</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hi <%= fullname %>,</div>
            
            <div class="intro-text">
                We're thrilled to have you join the SkillLink community! You've just unlocked access to a vibrant marketplace of talented students ready to bring their skills to your projects.
            </div>

            <div class="intro-text">
                Whether you're looking for design, development, writing, marketing, or any other skill, SkillLink makes it easy to find, connect with, and hire the perfect student for your needs.
            </div>

            <!-- Features Section -->
            <div class="features">
                <h2>What You Can Do on SkillLink</h2>
                
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Browse Student Profiles</h3>
                        <p>Explore portfolios, reviews, and skills to find the perfect match for your project.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Direct Communication</h3>
                        <p>Message students directly to discuss your project requirements and expectations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Quick & Easy Hiring</h3>
                        <p>Post your project or hire students directly with our streamlined process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">✨</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Quality Guaranteed</h3>
                        <p>Access verified student profiles with ratings and reviews from previous clients.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <div class="cta-container">
                <a href="[DASHBOARD_LINK]" class="cta-button">Start Exploring Talent</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Support Section -->
            <div class="support-text">
                Need help getting started? Check out our <a href="[HELP_CENTER_LINK]">Help Center</a> or reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@skilllink.com">support@skilllink.com</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="[TWITTER_LINK]">𝕏</a>
                <a href="[LINKEDIN_LINK]">in</a>
                <a href="[INSTAGRAM_LINK]">📷</a>
            </div>
            <p>
                <a href="[WEBSITE_LINK]">SkillLink.com</a> |
                <a href="[PRIVACY_LINK]">Privacy Policy</a> |
                <a href="[TERMS_LINK]">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 12px;">
                © 2025 SkillLink. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px;">
                You're receiving this email because you signed up for SkillLink.<br>
                <a href="[UNSUBSCRIBE_LINK]">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>